# ROBIN automation (Selenium / Maven)

## App under test
- URL: `https://auto-robin-qtr.santechture.com/ROBIN`
- User: `QFacilityAdmin` / `QFacilityAdmin123`

## Run tests (PowerShell)
```powershell
# All patient registration scenarios
mvn test "-Dtest=PatientRegistrationTestRunner" "-Dheaded=true"

# Single tag
mvn test "-Dtest=PatientRegistrationTestRunner" "-Dheaded=true" "-Dcucumber.filter.tags=@TestCase15 and @UI"

# Other suites
mvn test "-Dtest=AuditTestRunner" "-Dheaded=true"
mvn test "-Dtest=BillingTestRunner" "-Dheaded=true"
mvn test "-Dtest=TestRunner" "-Dheaded=true"
```

## MCP in Cursor
- **Playwright MCP** (`.cursor/mcp.json`): explore ROBIN UI, find locators, debug flows in a real browser from chat.
- **Browser MCP** (built-in): use `browser_navigate` → `browser_snapshot` → click/fill for quick UI checks without writing code first.

After editing `mcp.json`, open **Cursor Settings → Tools & MCP** and enable **playwright**, or restart Cursor.

## When adding scenarios
- Keep Gherkin in `resources/Features/`
- Reuse existing steps in `src/test/java/stepDefinitions/`
- Prefer stable IDs (`InvoiceForm:PatientTypeCash`, `AccumedPatientCreateForm:*`) over brittle XPath
